  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-41989fa4-ed25-44ef-91e5-98088df64a29\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9944995f-e65c-44c8-8eda-6b2b443e6167\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d8098e8a-ba21-4c71-9479-d569d5a0446a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d24c985d-8246-11ed-bbe3-e3ff59d4a48b\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>프로필명함 + 동영상 mp4</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cd7b0077-78f3-43b7-ace3-41ac10290fd7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d24c985e-8246-11ed-bbe3-8f2e1ba8c156\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">오늘은 프로필명함을 제작해주신 분에게 파워포인트 애니메이션 효과를 입힌 동영상을 보여드리겠습니다. 아주 간단하고 저렴하게 자신의 프로필을 영상으로 만들어 드리는 서비스입니다. 프로필을 의뢰하신분께 완전 저렴한 비용으로 동영상을 만들어 mp4파일로 만들어 드립니다.</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d24c985f-8246-11ed-bbe3-d1cf2ccc7a45\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c208e5f1-a057-4d55-89c0-c7a280d75256\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d24cbf70-8246-11ed-bbe3-e3718d6d134b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-video se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-video se-section-align- se-l-default\" style=\"max-width:648px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-video\" id=\"SE-6d7e3a24-c57e-4eaa-9916-337d7cbb1397\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-c0ba98f2-77fa-4d70-8f0a-b20263e6386b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-938406b7-159e-4e50-8de3-154a3126a8c1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-01554605-17d2-4e84-902e-9cd4479994b2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d24ce681-8246-11ed-bbe3-69d478f53e78\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>프로필명함 + 동영상</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-398bb0bd-bd7f-4e01-9492-c3264a154336\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222963013175/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ad5e836b-feec-46f7-a354-9b6715b7d853\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d24ce682-8246-11ed-bbe3-3b7e1323faeb\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>모바일명함에 영상까지~</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1c18278d-1cb3-4804-9310-978836a229fa\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d24ce683-8246-11ed-bbe3-33159b4e88ee\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">프로필을 영상으로 만들어서 약 15초 내외로 만들어 드리는 서비스입니다. 물론 프로필명함만을 만들어 드릴 수도 있고 동영상까지 제작을 의뢰하셔도 됩니다. 동영상만을 제작하면 오히려 비용이 비싸질 수 있으니 유념하세요. 고객여러분이 생각하시는 비용 이하로 제작될 것입니다. (주)파파스컴퍼니은 템플릿화한 프로필디자인에 영상까지의 비용을 고객여러분이 생각하시는 비용 이하로 책정하여 진행중입니다. 많은 문의 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d8237dd2-40ee-4164-8024-dafd8eb71bb8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d24ce684-8246-11ed-bbe3-f333f03d6da5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-39b86330-b9d8-48c3-8222-f7c96c777398\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d24ce685-8246-11ed-bbe3-2924af326353\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">동영상 제작방법은 지금은 비용문제로 ppt 파워포인트 애니메이션으로만 제작했습니다. 나중에 프리미어나 기타 영상편집프로그램으로 발전시켜나갈 예정입니다. 동영상이  궁금하시다면 지난번에 올린 가대천자료를 참고해 주세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f9149e67-398a-4171-a436-69d865fdac19\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b6539e20-2788-4ea3-b1c0-0411c6ea600a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d24ce686-8246-11ed-bbe3-d3af0db33456\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4a5ae284-b914-449c-b3d4-bebb92f61a70\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c6de5a05-88de-4986-9315-c09292fd4758\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222963013175/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8aadf8c2-34b7-4b4b-929c-45ca23e650c2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222963013175/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ffd89842-1958-4bb8-9ef6-248bc89e91b8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222963013175/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fc7cca1d-23ce-4ba5-944e-3a46d6ab1131\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5001d583-e0ba-4b77-b1c1-2b219c648709\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d24d0d97-8246-11ed-bbe3-1d4e5b28370e\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">ppt는 내용과 템플릿에 따라 많은 변경이 이루어집니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c4546cda-f015-4cef-8d9e-f9b0bc0af50d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-video se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-video se-section-align- se-l-default\" style=\"max-width:648px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-video\" id=\"SE-1825653b-abc5-40ab-80a6-153d2e91ad9f\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d70fab02-16bf-4f64-ba5b-5e709c478744\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b6f17536-5649-46f2-ac3a-5dae1a153f20\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d24d0d98-8246-11ed-bbe3-379a86530629\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">2차 수정 때 조금 더 애니메이션을 가미해서 제작할 예정입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-530bfca5-d2ee-4c41-bc63-7f11bc20ee20\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d24d0d99-8246-11ed-bbe3-b30e1b02ddad\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">그리고 주문하시는 분께는 작업된 png, ppt, mp4파일 전부를 드릴 예정입니다. 많은 문의와 호응 부탁드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1457467a-847c-4384-ab31-9fa47b3070d5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d24d0d9a-8246-11ed-bbe3-53a399d7d19c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9b63bb97-7f00-4080-9e9c-3ed64a7a58e7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d24d34ab-8246-11ed-bbe3-bdcbea5ab3a3\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">참고로 종이면함과의 비교는 다음 사이트를 참고하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-608444f4-e9f5-41cb-9490-59e6ef3120fe\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d24d34ac-8246-11ed-bbe3-476378ed41ad\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-56659d6e-bd1d-4cc6-92f3-e52b312b0052\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align- se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
